OL,3,CTwo teenagers deny murder of 'loving
OL,4,Cfather' who was stabbed
OL,6,FTwo teenagers have pleaded not guilty
OL,7,Fto the murder of a 38-year-old dad in
OL,8,FBarry.
OL,10,FKamran Aman was found with a wound to
OL,11,Fthe torso on Barry Road, Barry just
OL,12,Fbefore midnight on June 30th.
OL,14,FAn inquest heard that Mr Aman died of
OL,15,Fa single stab wound to the chest.
OL,17,FThe two youths - who can't be named
OL,18,Fbecause of their age - denied a single
OL,19,Fcharge of murder at Merthyr Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Friday, 1 August.
