OL,3,CTwo teenagers deny murder of 'loving
OL,4,Cfather' who was stabbed
OL,6,FOne of the defendants was in court.
OL,7,FThe other appeared via videolink from
OL,8,Fa Young Offender Institution in
OL,9,FYorkshire.
OL,11,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clare remanded both
OL,12,Fdefendants in custody ahead of a trial
OL,13,Fdue to begin on 11 November, in front
OL,14,Fof Mr Justice Griffiths.
OL,16,FMr Aman's family released a tribute
OL,17,Ffollowing the incident, saying they
OL,18,Fmourned his loss with "profound
OL,19,Fsorrow".
